flowchart LR
    subgraph P[Publisher]
        TX[业务事务] --> WAL[WAL Records]
        WAL --> LD[Logical Decoding<br/>ReorderBuffer]
        PUB[Publication<br/>表/操作/行/列过滤] --> OUT[pgoutput]
        LD --> OUT
        SLOT[(Logical Slot<br/>restart_lsn<br/>confirmed_flush_lsn)] --> LD
        OUT --> WS[WAL Sender]
    end

    WS -->|Logical Replication Protocol| NET[(网络)]

    subgraph S[Subscriber]
        NET --> AW[Apply Worker]
        AW --> MAP[Relation 映射<br/>Replica Identity 查找]
        MAP --> TGT[(Subscriber Tables)]
        AW --> ORIGIN[(Replication Origin<br/>remote_lsn/local_lsn)]
        TS[Table Sync Worker] -->|Snapshot + COPY| TGT
        TS -->|专用临时 Sync Slot| P
        TGT --> SWAL[Subscriber WAL]
    end

    subgraph C[自定义 CDC Consumer]
        NET2[Replication Connection] --> DEC[pglogrepl 解码]
        DEC --> Q[有界队列/Backpressure]
        Q --> SINK[(幂等 Sink)]
        SINK --> CKPT[(Durable LSN Checkpoint)]
        CKPT -->|Standby Status Update| NET2
    end

    WS -.同一 pgoutput 数据源.-> NET2

    DDL[DDL / Sequence / 权限 / 扩展] -.不会自动复制.-> MANUAL[人工 Schema Evolution]
    FAIL[消费者停机/冲突/网络故障] --> SLOT
    SLOT -->|保留 WAL，可能写满磁盘| WAL
